desc: Bucker Creek Ranch is located in Dripping Springs, Texas. We offer Ranch to Market Wagyu Beef raised in the scenic hill country. Bucker Creek Ranch offers, Wagyu Steaks in numerous cuts, Wagyu Beef Jerky and Wagyu Beef Sticks in various flavors and a variety of Wagyu Dry Sausages.

layout.text:
A beef stick so good it ought
to be its own food group.

Wagyu beef in a snack stick? But we didn't stop there.
Jerky too because it's that good!
